sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant Health as Health Server<br/>8034/TCP Plaintext
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant TGIS as TGIS / caikit-nlp<br/>8033 or 8085/TCP gRPC
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI-compatible<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 1: Classification with Text Generation (v1 Unary)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Headers: passthrough + X-Forwarded-Access-Token
    activate Orch

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note right of Orch: Input Detection Phase
        Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
        Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>detector-id header, Optional TLS/mTLS
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (input)
    end

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note right of Orch: Generation Phase
        Orch->>TGIS: Generate RPC<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS<br/>Header passthrough
        TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note right of Orch: Output Detection Phase
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>detector-id header, Optional TLS/mTLS
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (output)
    end

    Orch-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>(generated text + detection results)
    deactivate Orch

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 2: OpenAI Chat Completions with Detection (v2)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Headers: passthrough
    activate Orch

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note right of Orch: Input Detection
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/chat<br/>detector-id header, Optional TLS/mTLS
        Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    end

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note right of Orch: Generation Phase
        Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Bearer token (api_token), Optional TLS
        OpenAI-->>Orch: Chat completion response (or SSE stream)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note right of Orch: Output Detection
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>detector-id header, Optional TLS/mTLS
        Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
    end

    Orch-->>Client: JSON or SSE Response<br/>(completion + detection results)
    deactivate Orch

    Note over Client,Health: Health Check Flow

    Client->>Health: GET /health (plaintext HTTP)
    Health-->>Client: 200 OK + package version info

    Client->>Health: GET /info (plaintext HTTP)
    Health-->>Client: 200 OK + downstream service health status
